&lt;p&gt;If you love connecting dots between strategy, spend, and operational excellence, and are the type to get a small thrill from a perfectly balanced tracker or a streamlined process — you’ll fit right in.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary lead for financial operations and business process workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and streamline the end-to-end purchase order (PO) lifecycle and invoicing schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain meticulous trackers, ensuring real-time visibility into project spend versus forecasts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and implement process improvements to drive operational efficiency and financial compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
